org.biojava.bio.seq.io

Class EmblLikeLocationParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.biojava.bio.seq.io.EmblLikeLocationParser
  • Deprecated. 
    Use org.biojavax.bio.seq.io framework instead

    public class EmblLikeLocationParser
extends Object
    EmblLikeLocationParser parses EMBL/Genbank style locations. Supported location forms: 
       123
  <123 or >123
  (123.567)
  (123.567)..789
   123..(567.789)
  (123.345)..(567.789)
   123..456
  <123..567 or 123..>567 or <123..>567
   123^567
   AL123465:(123..567)
    Since:
    1.2
    Author:
    Keith James, Greg Cox
